So remove the `*` operation in <https://github.com/SciML/SciMLBase.jl/blob/4a95d3d1bd42c7bd7c13b8babdc2ee61188fbf8b/src/operators/common_defaults.jl#L13-L16>? I.e., remove the `*` in the first line below:
```for op in (:*, :/, :\), T in (:AbstractArray, :Number)
  @eval Base.$op(L::AbstractDiffEqLinearOperator, x::$T) = $op(convert(AbstractMatrix,L), x)
  @eval Base.$op(x::$T, L::AbstractDiffEqLinearOperator) = $op(x, convert(AbstractMatrix,L))
end```

